==> IDENTIFY YOURSELF FIRST!

From:  Danny K. Gargus <dgargus@gurulink.com>

The possible reason for having a separate order page is because
there might be 2 different price structures.

It's possible that the appliance site your wanting to buy retail
parts/items from also has wholesale rates available for businesses
or dealers.

In summary, I agree that the option should come at the beginning of
the order and not at the point when you've already decided to buy. I
wouldn't take offense to this as the ecommerce software is most
likely written to perform/sequence the way that you've experienced.

