elsewhere.

This is my way of throwing a monkey wrench into the well-laid
marketing plans of those big, database-obsessed companies that want
to extract every little nugget of information out of their customers.

With regards from Martha Retallick, who doesn't need to know your
mother's maiden name...

Martha Retallick, LRP Designs
